<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Offer Letter - {{companyName}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #fff;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .logo-placeholder {
            width: 120px;
            height: 60px;
            border: 2px dashed #ccc;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #999;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .company-address {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .letter-content {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .greeting {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .offer-details {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #555;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #333;
        }
        .closing {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 60px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .signature-box {
            width: 45%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .signature-line {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            height: 50px;
        }
        .signature-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="logo-placeholder">
            Logo
        </div>
        <h1>{{companyName}}</h1>
        <div class="company-address">
            {{companyAddress}}<br>
            {{companyCity}}, {{companyState}} {{companyZip}}<br>
            {{companyPhone}} | {{companyEmail}}
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="letter-content">
        <div class="greeting">
            <p>Dear {{candidateName}},</p>
        </div>

        <p>We are pleased to offer you the position of <strong>{{position}}</strong> at {{companyName}}. After careful consideration of your application and interviews, we believe your skills and experience will be valuable to our team.</p>

        <div class="highlight">
            <p>This offer is contingent upon your acceptance of the terms and conditions outlined below, along with the successful completion of any required background checks and pre-employment screenings.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="offer-details">
            <h3>Employment Details:</h3>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Position:</span>
                <span class="detail-value">{{position}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Department:</span>
                <span class="detail-value">{{department}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Employment Type:</span>
                <span class="detail-value">{{employmentType}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Start Date:</span>
                <span class="detail-value">{{startDate}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Location:</span>
                <span class="detail-value">{{location}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Salary/Compensation:</span>
                <span class="detail-value">{{salary}}</span>
            </div>
            {{#if probationPeriod}}
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Probation Period:</span>
                <span class="detail-value">{{probationPeriod}}</span>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            {{#if reportingTo}}
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Reporting To:</span>
                <span class="detail-value">{{reportingTo}}</span>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
        </div>

        {{#if customTerms}}
        <div class="custom-terms">
            <h3>Additional Terms:</h3>
            <p>{{customTerms}}</p>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <div class="responsibilities">
            <h3>Key Responsibilities:</h3>
            <p>As {{position}}, you will be responsible for:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Contributing to our team's success through your expertise and dedication</li>
                <li>Collaborating with colleagues to achieve departmental and organizational goals</li>
                <li>Maintaining high standards of performance and professional conduct</li>
                <li>Continuously developing your skills and knowledge relevant to your role</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="next-steps">
            <h3>Next Steps:</h3>
            <p>Please review this offer carefully and let us know your decision within <strong>{{responseTime}}</strong> days of receiving this letter. To accept this offer, please sign and return a copy of this letter by email to {{companyEmail}}.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-info">
            <p>If you have any questions or need clarification regarding any aspect of this offer, please don't hesitate to contact us:</p>
            <p>Email: {{companyEmail}}<br>
            Phone: {{companyPhone}}</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="closing">
        <p>We are excited about the possibility of you joining our team and look forward to your positive response.</p>
        <p>Sincerely,<br>
        The HR Team<br>
        {{companyName}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="signature-box">
            <div class="signature-line"></div>
            <div class="signature-label">HR Team</div>
            <div class="signature-label">{{companyName}}</div>
            <div class="signature-label">Date: {{currentDate}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="signature-box">
            <div class="signature-line"></div>
            <div class="signature-label">Candidate Signature</div>
            <div class="signature-label">{{candidateName}}</div>
            <div class="signature-label">Date: _________________</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>This offer letter is confidential and intended solely for the named recipient. If you are not the intended recipient, please notify us immediately and destroy this document.</p>
        <p>© {{currentYear}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
